      <heading>Sat Jul 14 (Aidan)      :: &amp;RSome Useful (maybe) Information&amp;n</heading>
      <slot>1</slot>
      <level>199</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>
Some levelling formulas:

Practices:
(int + wis - 32)/4 plus a random addition of 3 to 5

Trains:
Everyone gets 1 train each level unless they have 255 trains, in which
case, they don't get any.
Additionally, there is a 25% chance of getting a second train. This is
not affected by stats.
Soldier and Adventurer have a 30% chance of 2 extra practices.
Thief, Craftsman, Wisdom have a 40% chance of 2 extra practices.
(if they aren't sparked or teachable, that is)

HP/Mana/Move for everyone (class bonus listed in next section):
5 to 14  + (con - 13)/4 (HP)
5 to 14  + (wis - 13)/4 (Mana)
3 to 5 + (dex -13)/4 (move)

Soldier and Adventurer:
+14 to hitpoints if sparked/teachable
if not: +14 + 1/4 of the mana they would have gotten had they been
sparked/teachable.

+3 to mana if sparked/teachable. None if not.

Thief/Craftsman/Wisdom:
+10 to hitpoints if sparked/teachable
if not: +10 + 1/4 of the mana they would have gotten had they been
sparked/teachable.

+5 to mana if sparked/teachable. None if not.

Channeler:
+4 to hitpoints.
+11 to mana.
Wilder:
+4 to hitpoints.
+15 to mana.


</text>
    </message>
