sooner. I'm much used to this board never being used. Anyways,
Jephrey wasn't soley fired because of his abuse of Newbiegoto, but that
isn't here or there to discuss. Abuse of Newbiegoto, truly, was only
made so that NGs in itself could help newbies out a little better. In
direct help with newbies, Newbiegoto Oval would be acceptable. But in
just a handy way to get to Balon or the Oval when nothing is happening?
Pishaw. It isn't likely that i'll catch you using the Oval alias
Pyralin, but in effect, it is abuse. I'd rather prefer that everyone
only use Newbiegoto in such instances that one of you says &quot;Newbiegoto
Donation&quot; and then you follow behind them. As for the question of the
alias, thats an alias. Everyone has access to an alias, but for
Newbiegoto? Not many, so thus, silly little rules.

